Documents to upload with the online application

     * Curriculum vitae
     * Letter of application
     * Bachelor school reports (transcript of grades) and certificate
     * Master school reports (transcript of grades) and certification when
       available
     * Letter(s) of recommendation(s): do not forget to mention (step 4 of
       the application process) the e-mail address of the professors who
       wish to send recommendation letters. They will receive an automatic
       email to upload their letter.

   Only Complete application will be considered.

   Applicants are invited to submit also any official documents attesting
   of their achievements (ranking, ranking in national and international
   competitions, etc.)

   Moreoever, the authors of the recommendation's letters are encouraged
   to provide if possible, elements of comparison that can be checked.

