2019 LAUREATES

   Bao Viet Le Hung, 6 months at LAGA. (Assistant professor at the
   Northwestern University) His research interests are Galois
   representations, Automorphic forms, Arithmetic geometry and their
   interactions, Moduli spaces of Galois and related aspects in modular
   and geometric representation theory.
     __________________________________________________________________

